    "The remainder of this paper is structured as follows.",
    "Sect. 2 includes a description of the SLR stages and their relationship with AI.",
    "Section 3 outlines the methodology we employed to identify the SLR tools discussed in the survey.",
    "Section 4 provides a metareview of previous surveys about SLR tools that analysed AI features.",
    "Section 5 provides an in-depth examination of the 21 tools."
  ]
